Clawd is the definition of content creator. From standing on the block selling CD’s with his music all the way to acting and producing films, @jonclawd has made every piece of content you can think of. 

He had a chance to tell his story.. How it all started… mistakes and bumps in the road.. what shaped him to be who is is today.. 

He also dropped a bunch of gems relative to both the film and music industry. 

No this ain’t John singleton (RIP) … This Jon Clawd !
